sourcesContent:
export const groupingMap = [
    {
        label: "Primary",
        color: "primary",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "region",
                data: "REGION",
                label: "Region",
                type: "dropdown",
                initialValue: "Not Specified",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                data: "NAME",
                label: "Name",
                type: "text",
                readonly: true,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: false,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "etat",
                data: "STATUS",
                label: "ETAT",
                type: "dropdown",
                initialValue: "Ready",
                allowInvalid: false,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                data: "ARCHIVED",
                label: "Archived",
                type: "dropdown",
                initialValue: "No",
                readOnly: true,
                mandatory: true,
                manually: false,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "oldAggrSite",
                data: "OLDAGGRSITE",
                label: "OLD Aggreg site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                id: "newAggrSite",
                data: "NEWAGGRSITE",
                label: "NEW Aggreg site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                id: "radioSite",
                data: "RADIOSITE",
                label: "Radio Site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                data: "REVISIONNUMBER",
                label: "Revision Number",
                type: "numeric",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: false,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                id: "project",
                data: "PROJECT",
                label: "Project",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "transmissionType",
                data: "TRANSMISSIONTYPE",
                label: "Transmission Type",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "dateIng",
                data: "DATEING",
                label: "Date ING",
                type: "date",
                dateFormat: "DD/MM/YYYY",
                datePickerConfig: {
                    firstDay: 1
                },
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "siteTechnology",
                data: "SITETECHNOLOGY",
                label: "Site Technology",
                type: "dropdown",
                initialValue: "2G/3G/4G",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Information",
        color: "info",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                data: "COMMENTS",
                label: "Comments",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Microwave Part",
        color: "info",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "sVlan",
                data: "SVLAN",
                label: "SVLAN",
                type: "numeric",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "techMwSite",
                data: "TECHMWSITE",
                label: "TECH MW SITE",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "mwEquip",
                data: "MWEQUIP",
                label: "MW Equipment",
                type: "dropdown",
                source: [],
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 250
            },
            {
                id: "mwPort",
                data: "MWPORT",
                label: "MW Port",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "technoMwAggre",
                data: "TECHNOMWAGGRE",
                label: "TECHNO MW AGGRE",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "mwEquipmentAggre",
                data: "MWEQUIPMENTAGGRE",
                label: "MW EQUIPMENT AGGRE",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "mwPortAggre",
                data: "MWPORTAGGRE",
                label: "MW PORT AGGRE",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "mwPortAggreDesc",
                data: "MWPORTAGGREDESC",
                label: "MW PORT AGGRE DESCR",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "SDH Part",
        color: "radio",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "RaccordementSdhSite",
                data: "RACCORDEMENTSDHSITE",
                label: "Raccordement SDH Site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "sdhEquipment",
                data: "SDHEQUIPMENT",
                label: "SDH Equipment",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "sdhEquipmentPortType",
                data: "SDHEQUIPMENTPORTTYPE",
                label: "SDH Equipment PORT TYPE",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "sdhEquipmentPortDesc",
                data: "SDHEQUIPMENTPORTDESC",
                label: "SDH Equipment PORT DESC",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "raccordementSdhAggreSite",
                data: "RACCORDEMENTSDHAGGRESITE",
                label: "Raccordement SDH AGGRE Site",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "sdhAggreEquipment",
                data: "SDHAGGREEQUIPMENT",
                label: "SDH AGGRE Equipment",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "sdhEquipmentPortAggreDesc",
                data: "SDHEQUIPMENTPORTAGGREDESC",
                label: "SDH Equipment PORT AGGRE DESC",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "FO Part",
        color: "radio",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "ticketNumber",
                data: "TICKETNUMBER",
                label: "Ticket Number",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "portSite",
                data: "PORTSITE",
                label: "PORT SITE",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "portAggre",
                data: "PORTAGGRE",
                label: "PORT AGGRE",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "IP Part",
        color: "radio",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "ipTechno",
                data: "IPTECHNO",
                label: "IP TECHNO",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "ipEquipment",
                data: "IPEQUIPMENT",
                label: "IP EQUIPMENT",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "ipPort",
                data: "IPPORT",
                label: "IP PORT",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "ipPortDescr",
                data: "IPPORTDESCR",
                label: "IP PORT DESCR",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "Radio Side",
        color: "radio",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "type",
                data: "TYPE",
                label: "Type",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "boardType",
                data: "BOARDTYPE",
                label: "Board Type",
                type: "dropdown",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "om",
                data: "OM",
                label: "O&M",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                id: "nbIp",
                data: "NBIP",
                label: "NB IP",
                type: "text",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                id: "Gw",
                data: "GW",
                label: "GW",
                type: "text",
                //validator: "ipValidator",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                id: "mask",
                data: "MASK",
                label: "Mask",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                id: "2emeIp",
                data: "2emeIp",
                label: "2eme IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                id: "ntpIp",
                data: "NTPIP",
                label: "NTP IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                id: "ntpGw",
                data: "NTPGW",
                label: "NTP GW",
                //validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            }

        ]
    },
    {
        label: "RNC Side",
        color: "rnc",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "rncName",
                data: "RNCNAME",
                label: "RNC Name",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            },
            {
                id: "rncPort",
                data: "RNCPORT",
                label: "RNC PORT",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 150
            },
            {
                id: "rncIp",
                data: "RNCIP",
                label: "RNC IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 100
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        label: "2G Site Side",
        color: "site2g",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [
            {
                id: "bscName",
                data: "BSCNAME",
                label: "BSC Name",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: false,
                width: 120
            },
            {
                id: "bscPort",
                data: "BSCPORT",
                label: "BSC PORT",
                type: "text",
                mandatory: true,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                id: "bscIp",
                data: "BSCIP",
                label: "BSC IP",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                initialValue: "10.137.0.0",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 110
            },
            {
                id: "bscNextHopIp",
                data: "BSCNEXTHOPIP",
                label: "Next Hope BSC",
                validator: "ipValidator",
                type: "text",
                initialValue: "10.137.0.0",
                mandatory: false,
                manually: true,
                width: 130
            }
        ]
    }
];
